name: Nassau
absentee_method: Merged into voters' home precincts AFTER election night
nyt_race_description_race: Jackie Gordon, a public-school teacher and a 29-year veteran of the Army Reserve, is the Democrat vying against Andrew Garbarino, a Republican state assemblyman, for the former seat of Representative Peter T. King, a 14-term Republican and Trump supporter who opted against another term.
poll_display_race: Polls close at 9 p.m. Eastern time.
expectations_text_race: Only unofficial results from in-person early and Election Day voting were released on election night. Mail ballots, which have until Nov. 10 to arrive if postmarked by Election Day, will be reported in the following days and weeks. It took weeks to finish counting ballots during the state's June primary.
expectations_text_short_race: Only unofficial results from in-person early and Election Day voting were released on election night. Mail ballots will be reported in the following days and weeks.
